    "body": "it's missing this:\n\n``` diff\n--- a/mods/ts/mod.yaml\n+++ b/mods/ts/mod.yaml\n@@ -202,6 +202,9 @@ Fonts:\n        Title:\n                Font:./mods/common/FreeSansBold.ttf\n                Size:32\n+       MediumBold:\n+               Font:./mods/common/FreeSansBold.ttf\n+               Size:18\n        BigBold:\n                Font:./mods/common/FreeSansBold.ttf\n                Size:24\ndiff --git a/mods/ts/rules/world.yaml b/mods/ts/rules/world.yaml\nindex 05a4496..031aa8a 100644\n--- a/mods/ts/rules/world.yaml\n+++ b/mods/ts/rules/world.yaml\n@@ -178,4 +178,6 @@ World:\n        ScreenShaker:\n        RadarPings:\n        StartGameNotification:\n+       ObjectivesPanel:\n+               PanelName: SKIRMISH_STATS\n```\n\nBut FWIW, I kinda like it that way. I certainly use the debug cheats more often than I'd like to see the scores when I'm in ts.\n"
